description:
NOTES: As with the last after show rip this one has problems, too. All of the video is there but it has some weird frame stuff. Like every once in a while a frame will appear from another part of the video. The stream has this defect, too. So this is as good as it gets. It's totally watchable though. 

Also WTF Kennedy how did you barely even mention Rand Paul?
